        "content": "<p>We have two typeclasses, <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/find/t2_space\">docs#t2_space</a> and <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/find/separated_space\">docs#separated_space</a>. These propositions are equivalent but the latter needs a uniform space structure to be defined. Some lemmas assume <code>[t2_space X]</code>, some assume <code>[separated_space X]</code>. I suggest that we drop <code>separated_space</code> and replace it with a custom constructor for <code>t2_space</code>.</p>",
